Otras dos métricas que puedo agregar, precision and recal:

"Intuitively, precision is the ability of the classifier not to label as
positive a sample that is negative, and recall is the ability of the classifier
to find all the positive samples."

Extraído de (https://scikit-learn.org/dev/modules/model_evaluation.html#precision-recall-and-f-measures)

